	<h2 id="location">Location Services</h2>
	<p>Some services on this site make use of location-based data. If you allow these services, we will collect information about the Wi-fi routers closest to you and the cell IDs of the towers closest to you. We use this information to provide the requested location-based service, not to identify you. You will be asked for your permission each time a location-based service is requested. You may opt-out of location based services at any time by editing the setting at the device level or by contacting us.
	</p>
	<h2 id="collection">Collection and Use</h2>
	<p>Before or at the time of collecting personal information, we will identify the purposes for which information is being collected. We collect personal information from you such as your name, email address, and phone number.</p>
	<p>When you download and use our services, we automatically collect information on the type of device you use, operating system version, device identifier (or "UDID"), name, grade, profile picture and school name and location.</p>
	<p>We will collect and use your personal information solely with the objective of fulfilling those purposes specified by us such as to administer your account, respond to your requests,and provide location-based services.</p>
	<p>Personal data should be relevant to the purposes for which it is to be used, and, to the extent necessary for those purposes, should be accurate, complete, and up-to-date. If your personal information changes, or if you no longer desire our service, you may correct, update, amend, delete/remove, or deactivate it by making the change on our member information page or by emailing our customer support at chatpassme@gmail.com.</p>
	<p>We will only retain personal information and location information as long as necessary for the fulfillment of those purposes and as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.</p>
	<h2 id="sharing">Sharing your Information</h2>
	<p>We will share your personal information with third parties only in the ways that are described in this privacy policy.  We do not sell your personal information to third parties. We may provide your personal information to companies that provide services to help us with our business activities such as email service provider or hosting provider. These companies are authorized to use your personal information only as necessary to provide these services to us.</p>
	<p>We may also disclose your personal information as required by law, such as to comply with a subpoena, or similar legal process and when we believe in good faith that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, protect your safety or the safety of others, investigate fraud, or respond to a government request.</p>
	<h2 id="tracking">Tracking and Ads</h2>
	<p>Both first and third-party cookies are present on this site. These tracking technologies are used:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>To customize the user experience to your tastes and interests</li>
		<li>To gauge the effectiveness of customer communications and marketing campaigns</li>
		<li>By third parties to provide behavioral-based advertising</li>
		<li>By third parties to analyze advertising interest and effectiveness</li>
	</ul>
	<h2 id="security">Security</h2>
	<p> The security of your personal information is important to us. We will protect personal information by reasonable security safeguards against loss or theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use or modification. We follow generally accepted industry standards to protect the personal information submitted to us, both during transmission and once we receive it. No method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security. If you have any questions about security on our web site, you can contact us at chatpassme@gmail.com</p>
